1
00:01:09,820 --> 00:01:13,500
=Inherently Kind=

2
00:01:14,780 --> 00:01:17,700
=Episode 6=
(Am I Not Gu Qingmei?)

3
00:01:21,599 --> 00:01:23,920
Being a female CEO is
already tiring enough.

4
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:27,239
And then He Jinchen said tonight

5
00:01:27,560 --> 00:01:28,799
he wanted to throw me
a birthday banquet,

6
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:31,040
inviting a bunch of socialites
and wealthy ladies.

7
00:01:32,599 --> 00:01:35,359
I don't even remember my birthday.

8
00:01:36,000 --> 00:01:37,879
How could I possibly remember
all the etiquette?

9
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:40,599
Should I do a practice run with you?

10
00:01:43,560 --> 00:01:45,079
Mr. Mu, are we

11
00:01:45,280 --> 00:01:46,879
starting class now?

12
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,159
First is the toast.

13
00:01:55,959 --> 00:01:56,599
This is not the way.

14
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:03,920
Pinch with your fingers.

15
00:02:08,280 --> 00:02:09,000
45 degrees.

16
00:02:10,520 --> 00:02:11,039
Cheers.

17
00:02:14,159 --> 00:02:16,199
Then look at the bottom of the glass.

18
00:02:30,360 --> 00:02:32,400
An'an is having so much fun!

19
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:34,080
(Happy Birthday)

20
00:02:34,080 --> 00:02:35,520
My wife is the most beautiful!

21
00:02:59,039 --> 00:02:59,520
Great.

22
00:03:01,319 --> 00:03:03,159
(Isn't that Luya's limited edition
for this season?)

23
00:03:03,879 --> 00:03:05,080
(Even I could not get it.)

24
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:06,680
(How did she get it?)

25
00:03:14,520 --> 00:03:15,719
Gu Qingmei today

26
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,560
looks completely different.

27
00:03:17,840 --> 00:03:20,479
She is now the Chairman
of Gu Corporation.

28
00:03:20,719 --> 00:03:22,120
Of course her demeanor has changed.

29
00:03:25,120 --> 00:03:27,360
Thank you all for coming to

30
00:03:27,879 --> 00:03:30,759
my wife, Gu Qingmei's birthday banquet.

31
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:31,919
Now,

32
00:03:32,479 --> 00:03:33,960
let us officially begin.

33
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:36,039
Alright.

34
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:39,759
Please.

35
00:03:54,439 --> 00:03:54,840
Bring it in.

36
00:04:08,759 --> 00:04:09,280
(Madam Gu,)

37
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,800
(this is our diamond necklace.)

38
00:04:10,919 --> 00:04:11,599
(Please take a look.)

39
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,439
(This piece here,)

40
00:04:42,439 --> 00:04:44,480
(it's China Red with ocean pearls.)

41
00:04:45,600 --> 00:04:46,439
(It's completely)

42
00:04:46,560 --> 00:04:48,360
(made of genuine ocean pearls.)

43
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:49,600
(It's stunning)

44
00:04:49,839 --> 00:04:50,879
(and elegant as well.)

45
00:04:59,000 --> 00:04:59,759
(It suits you well.)

46
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:03,600
(Mr. Mu, your tuition is so expensive.)

47
00:05:03,959 --> 00:05:04,839
(I cannot afford it.)

48
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,199
(Just buy me a meal.)

49
00:05:17,879 --> 00:05:20,399
Gu Qingmei has really become capable!

50
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:22,480
Even Jinchen is obssessed with her.

51
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,920
What kind of occasion is this?

52
00:05:26,879 --> 00:05:28,040
Don't spoil the mood!

53
00:05:32,759 --> 00:05:33,600
Dear,

54
00:05:33,879 --> 00:05:35,519
it's been ages
since you buy me gift last time.

55
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:37,680
Be good.

56
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,439
Next birthday,

57
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,519
you'll get something more precious.

58
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:40,920
That's better.

59
00:05:47,959 --> 00:05:48,480
Qingmei.

60
00:05:50,399 --> 00:05:51,079
Happy birthday.

61
00:05:52,399 --> 00:05:53,040
Thank you.

62
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:55,959
You probably don't know him yet.

63
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,639
This is my future son-in-law,

64
00:05:57,839 --> 00:05:58,759
Mu Shaoze.

65
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:01,759
He is also the second largest
shareholder of Shengda Group.

66
00:06:02,399 --> 00:06:03,720
He just returned to
develop his career here.

67
00:06:04,759 --> 00:06:06,639
This couple is a perfect match!

68
00:06:06,720 --> 00:06:08,240
When are you going to
invite us to the wedding?

69
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,439
Soon, soon!

70
00:06:10,199 --> 00:06:10,959
Sorry, everyone.

71
00:06:14,360 --> 00:06:17,120
Jinxi and I are still
getting to know each other.

72
00:06:19,160 --> 00:06:19,759
Exactly.

73
00:06:20,120 --> 00:06:21,279
My mom is just being impatient.

74
00:06:21,639 --> 00:06:23,759
We are still young,
so we need to spend some time together.

75
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:26,360
Jinxi is getting engaged soon.

76
00:06:28,839 --> 00:06:29,480
Alright, alright.

77
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,639
Everyone, enjoy.

78
00:06:30,839 --> 00:06:31,680
Enjoy the party.

79
00:06:32,639 --> 00:06:33,480
Enjoy the party.

80
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:34,519
Alright, alright.

81
00:06:39,839 --> 00:06:41,800
Let us have a toast!

82
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:43,439
Alright, alright!

83
00:06:43,519 --> 00:06:44,920
Cheers, cheers!

84
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:05,680
Are you alright?

85
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:07,480
I am fine.

86
00:07:09,759 --> 00:07:11,800
Shaoze, thank you for saving her.

87
00:07:12,959 --> 00:07:13,600
It's my duty.

88
00:07:16,639 --> 00:07:17,199
An'an!

89
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:17,759
An'an!

90
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:18,120
An'an!

91
00:07:18,199 --> 00:07:18,759
An'an!

92
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:19,319
What do we do?

93
00:07:19,319 --> 00:07:20,079
An'an, are you alright?

94
00:07:20,199 --> 00:07:21,439
Call an ambulance, now!

95
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:22,000
Alright.

96
00:07:23,360 --> 00:07:24,160
I can save him!

97
00:07:26,040 --> 00:07:26,560
Come on.

98
00:07:34,000 --> 00:07:34,920
Let go of my grandson!

99
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:36,399
Are you going to harm my grandson?

100
00:07:37,519 --> 00:07:38,800
She is performing the Heimlich maneuver.

101
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,639
She needs some time.

102
00:07:42,120 --> 00:07:42,639
An'an.

103
00:07:43,759 --> 00:07:44,279
An'an.

104
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,040
An'an.

105
00:07:46,120 --> 00:07:46,759
Are you alright?

106
00:07:47,279 --> 00:07:48,279
Mommy!

107
00:07:48,800 --> 00:07:49,959
I'm so scared!

108
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:53,399
Mommy is so scared!

109
00:07:54,519 --> 00:07:55,680
It's alright, it's alright.

110
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:58,879
It's alright, it's alright.

111
00:08:11,040 --> 00:08:12,120
Sorry... I'm so sorry.

112
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:14,079
Reporter Su?

113
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:17,120
(The documents are all with me.)

114
00:08:17,319 --> 00:08:18,319
(You should be the one to reveal it.)

115
00:08:20,199 --> 00:08:21,360
(Please don't tell anyone
it came from me.)

116
00:08:24,639 --> 00:08:25,480
It's you!

117
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:28,079
You...

118
00:08:28,240 --> 00:08:28,839
Stop!

119
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:34,039
Reporter Su?

120
00:08:35,879 --> 00:08:37,120
Could it be that I am
really not Gu Qingmei?

121
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,240
Qingmei.

122
00:08:40,159 --> 00:08:40,960
What's going on?

123
00:08:42,559 --> 00:08:43,159
Nothing.

124
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:44,919
I just sprained my ankle.

125
00:08:46,600 --> 00:08:47,399
Then let's go home.

126
00:08:52,960 --> 00:08:53,440
Boss.

127
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,519
We found the woman.

128
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:56,720
Her name is Su Li.

129
00:08:57,159 --> 00:08:58,200
She is a journalist for Deep News.

130
00:08:59,159 --> 00:09:00,000
Su Li?

131
00:09:00,519 --> 00:09:01,000
Yes.

132
00:09:01,720 --> 00:09:02,480
Her pen name is Su Su.

133
00:09:03,279 --> 00:09:04,159
Before the car accident,

134
00:09:04,279 --> 00:09:04,799
she had been investigating

135
00:09:04,879 --> 00:09:06,679
the dark secrets behind cosmetic
raw materials of Meiyan International.

136
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:08,840
The informant who gave her the message

137
00:09:09,039 --> 00:09:10,519
was supposed to meet us here tonight.

138
00:09:10,840 --> 00:09:12,080
But he stood us up.

139
00:09:12,639 --> 00:09:13,600
Now he's not answering his phone either.

140
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:15,279
Keep trying.

141
00:09:16,159 --> 00:09:16,960
Increase the offer.

142
00:09:18,879 --> 00:09:20,159
Now that it has been confirmed

143
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:21,360
that Meiyan International

144
00:09:22,039 --> 00:09:23,879
is still using prohibited ingredients,

145
00:09:24,679 --> 00:09:25,399
it means

146
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:27,919
he may have more evidence in his hands.

147
00:09:29,480 --> 00:09:31,320
Otherwise, he would not be so cautious.

148
00:09:41,919 --> 00:09:42,440
(Dad.)

149
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:45,200
(This is your favorite cigar.)

150
00:09:46,919 --> 00:09:48,039
(Once I uncover the truth,)

151
00:09:49,399 --> 00:09:50,759
(I will pay my respects properly.)

152
00:09:57,879 --> 00:09:59,879
If I am not Gu Qingmei,

153
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:02,519
then why do I look exactly like her?

154
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:04,279
And why did I take her place?

155
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:07,720
Maybe the answer is in the diary.

156
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:11,799
Where is the diary?

157
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:18,360
Who took the diary?

158
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:21,879
Who could it be?

159
00:10:28,159 --> 00:10:28,759
This is...

160
00:10:34,080 --> 00:10:35,039
No matter who you are,

161
00:10:35,559 --> 00:10:36,399
I will find you!

162
00:10:41,759 --> 00:10:43,440
Is Gu Qingmei capable of that?

163
00:10:48,360 --> 00:10:50,480
(This family is far more
complicated than I imagined.)

164
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,080
Qingmei!

165
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,360
In the middle of the night,

166
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,639
what is that noise?

167
00:11:24,679 --> 00:11:25,200
What happened?

168
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:29,679
What is going on?

169
00:11:29,840 --> 00:11:30,679
What happened?

170
00:11:32,080 --> 00:11:33,759
What are you doing
in the middle of the night?

171
00:11:34,559 --> 00:11:36,039
You're bothering everyone
who's trying to sleep.

172
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:38,159
Where are your manners?

173
00:11:39,799 --> 00:11:41,559
Someone pushed me down just now!

174
00:11:42,440 --> 00:11:44,519
You better step forward right now!

175
00:11:47,399 --> 00:11:48,600
Or I'll be reviewing the footage.

176
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,159
Qingmei.

177
00:11:51,399 --> 00:11:52,840
For a wealthy family,

178
00:11:53,000 --> 00:11:54,320
privacy is of utmost importance.

179
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:56,679
Except for certain areas,
no cameras are installed.

180
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,879
You woke up the entire family
in the middle of the night,

181
00:11:58,919 --> 00:11:59,639
what do you want?

182
00:12:00,159 --> 00:12:00,720
Is that so?

183
00:12:01,960 --> 00:12:03,519
Then the He family's camera setup

184
00:12:03,559 --> 00:12:04,840
is quite interesting.

185
00:12:06,039 --> 00:12:06,600
Qingmei.

186
00:12:07,120 --> 00:12:08,480
Are you sure you're not seeing things?

187
00:12:11,639 --> 00:12:12,440
Alright.

188
00:12:12,799 --> 00:12:14,399
Let's end this here.

189
00:12:15,480 --> 00:12:16,440
Everyone go back to rest.

190
00:12:19,720 --> 00:12:21,720
Clean up the mess yourself!

191
00:12:25,679 --> 00:12:26,120
Let's go.

192
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,440
You don't believe me, do you?

193
00:12:37,159 --> 00:12:37,840
Never mind.

194
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:41,279
I will find the person myself!

195
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,799
(Why do you always feel so familiar,)

196
00:12:52,240 --> 00:12:54,759
(yet like a stranger?)

197
00:13:01,399 --> 00:13:02,720
(You're done with work?)

198
00:13:08,940 --> 00:13:11,700
(The pool is my paradise,
and also my hell.)

199
00:13:12,759 --> 00:13:13,759
The pool?

200
00:13:14,600 --> 00:13:15,519
What does that mean?

201
00:13:36,420 --> 00:13:41,180
♪Time stole the proof of our love♪

202
00:13:41,180 --> 00:13:46,020
♪Hidden in the moonlight,
lost in the clouds♪

203
00:13:46,020 --> 00:13:50,580
♪Tangled glances and love fall together♪

204
00:13:50,580 --> 00:13:55,500
♪Into a spiral of thoughts,
memories rewinding♪

205
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:59,300
♪Feelings both strange and familiar♪

206
00:13:59,300 --> 00:14:04,100
♪I just know you're
where my heart belongs♪

207
00:14:04,100 --> 00:14:06,940
♪Can't remember when
this flutter started♪

208
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:09,620
♪Or how it's supposed to end♪

209
00:14:09,980 --> 00:14:15,540
♪Goodbye to the world rushing in♪

210
00:14:15,940 --> 00:14:22,740
♪Let me hide in your eyes
and never leave♪

211
00:14:23,020 --> 00:14:27,700
♪Feel the rhythm of your heartbeat♪

212
00:14:27,860 --> 00:14:34,660
♪Every tomorrow seems worth the wait♪

213
00:14:34,980 --> 00:14:41,780
♪Let me fill the emptiness of a century♪

214
00:14:41,980 --> 00:14:46,460
♪As the wind brushes past your hem♪

215
00:14:46,460 --> 00:14:49,820
♪All my hidden feelings come undone♪

216
00:14:49,820 --> 00:14:56,740
♪Right as I confess my love♪
